U.K. stocks retreated as the shares
of Barclays Plc, Fresnillo Plc and Essar Energy Plc declined.  The benchmark FTSE 100 Index slipped 0.2 percent to
5,650.91 at 8:39 a.m. in London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
